---
title: Boxes
---

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h1>Boxes</h1>
    <p>Boxes are intended to create division amongst sections across the UI. To create boxes, we wrap content in <code>section.Box</code>. Boxes do not have any built-in margin.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-4">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <section class="Box">
      <h3>Here is a headline</h3>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam commodo ullamcorper sem non bibendum. Nunc sit amet tincidunt augue, nec commodo erat. Nam pulvinar, dui interdum condimentum interdum, felis risus tempor dui, quis volutpat tortor tellus vel quam.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-7">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <pre>
      <code><%= display_code('
<section class="Box">
  <h3>Here is a headline</h3>
  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet...</p>
</section>') %></code>
    </pre>
  </div>
</div>